    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Material comprising the leaf of any of several plants of the genus Nicotiana, of the nightshade family, dried and variously prepared, yielding a sedative and narcotic substance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
